Advancement
Necromancers can advance their studies of the dark arts in the
~>GuildHouse<~, or through the use of the ~>nritual<~ command. There are
a total of twenty-five guild levels. A Necromancer cannot advance their
guild level above their normal level. Additionally, they will need to
possess a fair amount of training to reach the upper guild levels. This
requirement is based on the Necromancer's intelligence and wisdom, and
to a lesser extent, their charisma and constitution.
